[BCFlags "1f"]
[RotationNote "Board 4, chOption: W, chBasis: N, basisKind:Declarer, nOption:3, nBasis: 0, nRot: 3, useStandardVul: true"]
[Category "Partnership Bidding"]
[Difficulty "advanced"]
[SkillPath "partnership_bidding/advanced_forcing"]
[Student "S"]
{WEST has no reason to consider Fourth Suit Forcing with this hand.

EAST does not have four \Ss or he would have already supported.

So WEST should bid the Notrump game.}

